{"tid":2062221,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財經台隨機騙局之分身","createTime":"2020-06-13T03:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T04:36:11.000Z","uid":161374,"like":50,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"18a6d8a36f2899e6597f342cf6902653a115e7a4","tid":2062221,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T03:59:38.000Z","msg":"玩得分身其實就好易玩<br />\n<br />\n分身1 吹奏股票A<br />\n分身2吹奏股票A<br />\n分身3吹奏股票B<br />\n分身4吹奏股股B<br />\n<br />\n股票A中咗<br />\n<br />\n就只用分身1同2 再分別吹奏股票C,D<br />\n然後用分身3，4吹奏分身1，2<br />\n<br />\n最後分身1嘅股票C中咗，再用分身2，3，4吹奏分身1<br />\n<br />\n分身一多，例如8個或16個分身咁就可以做到次次都講中咁<br />\n最後現真面目開班或收廣告費<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家要小心，由其由頭到尾都無貼過倉而又同你介紹股票嘅會員</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上內容純粹分享，無影射任何會員嘅意思，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只希望大家有獨立思考！</span></span>"},{"pid":"645613e6baa3a144a5735a1838f1fd53f36bb35b","tid":2062221,"uid":105833,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"同之前賭波tips一樣"},{"pid":"5200743da40e3674f3c4af80397d90f1bdf81bbe","tid":2062221,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"有咩著數"},{"pid":"86feb481d7b62f865279ec404103ce55c368d732","tid":2062221,"uid":161374,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"645613e6baa3a144a5735a1838f1fd53f36bb35b","tid":2062221,"uid":105833,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"同之前賭波tips一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:05:52.000Z","msg":"無錯，同一原理，但可惜一樣會有人中招<br />\n見到有人用完分身之後仲咁多fans 有感而發"},{"pid":"8849c2f8bedb7bbb3637d495822fb69a27c3ff1e","tid":2062221,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"86feb481d7b62f865279ec404103ce55c368d732","tid":2062221,"uid":161374,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"645613e6baa3a144a5735a1838f1fd53f36bb35b","tid":2062221,"uid":105833,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy